---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Cloud Native Architecture
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Patterns to provide scalability, speed, safety

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scalability
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- horizontal (preferred): scale infrastructure, more servers
- vertical: scale resources, more cpu, diskspace, memory

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Virtualization
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- tool to create resource elasticity
- increase number of virtual boxes, memory processors, etc. for a deployed app

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Visibility
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- monitor, alerts, dasboards

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Fault isolation and tolerance
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Context bounded applications: applications shouldn’t have any dependencies
  between each other

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Failover & Recovery
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- continuously deploying an application shouldn’t affect the entire system
- think about auto-recovery,
- the entire system is capable of identifying the failure and recover

